                    h4  Power Apps 
                    p   Built on SharePoint lists as database, aided by Power Automate. All were built within one Office365 tenant. 
                    h5 2021
                    details
                        summary Corporate management of change form digitalisation
                        p A management of change process, used to recording administrative changes at a corporate level, had existed, and was carried out using documents in .docx and .xlsx. Description were filled out in .docx, and outcomes of risk workshops were tabulated in .xlsx. Users needed to consult the company procedure or refer to the global QHSE manager for guidance. The management of the process itself was done through an Excel sheet (recording titles, unique ID numbers to MOCs, etc. )
                        p This app was a digital manifestation of the same process. Numbering to new MOCs was automatically assigned, and registering of MOC register was kept up to date automatically. Practical usage of the tool was guided through on-screen prompts, and the user journey through the process was guided by the application logic itself. 

                    details
                        summary "Amazing Race" companion mobile app with QR code scanner
                        p Companion app to an "Amazing Race" style of game, for an office teambuilding afternoon. Participating teams race on foot from one location to another. At each location, they must complete a challenge. Upon clearing a challenge, the team is given a QR code that they scan to receive a clue for the next location.
                        p The app also facilitates photo-taking at intervals. All photos are sent to a central SharePoint location, where it is available for all participants to view after the event. 
                    
                    details
                        summary Building visitor/employee sign-in tablet app
                        p App to allow visitors to sign themselves in on a tablet at reception and notify their host of their arrival. 
                        p Built to replace a third-party system. 
                    
                    h5 2020
                    details
                        summary QHSE site dropped objects inspection tablet app
                        p Tablet app that can be taken by an operator on an offshore vessel or plant facility to perform dropped objects inspections. 
                        p Inspection scope can be loaded. Each line item in the inspection can be marked off, have comments added to it, and have a photo attached to it. 
                        p App sequencing optimised for use outside of internet range. 
                        p Traditional "tabular" export of results in HTML also created, to replicate historical report formats. 
                        p Accompanied by a Power BI report for managerial oversight on inspection results and actions. 
                        p Startup required extensive Power Query manipulation to import existing data into the format required by new system.

                    details
                        summary Mentor-mentee matcher
                        p "Tinder for mentoring."
                        p Enter app to sign up, either as a prospective mentor or prospective mentee. Once signed up, view profiles of other members who have signed up. If seeking a mentor, the app allows for requesting mentorship. 
                        p Once relationship is established, there are facilities for capturing objectives and to take notes for meeting
                        
                    details 
                        summary Document review and approval by multiple reviewers in sequence
                        p Power Apps translation of an existing form in InfoPath. App facilitates the entry of a single form by multiple contributors, with multiple stage gates, and revision control. 
                        p App user base is divided into four distinct "roles". The form interface is different depending on which "role" is viewing. 
                        p App allow for form entry, edit, and displaying what stage the form is up to. 

                    details
                        summary Business case proforma
                        p Web-based app as a pro forma for writing business cases to aid in corporate-level decision-making. The pro forma includes a questionnaire, where every answer is given a score. Every business case results in an aggregated "benefit score" and "effort score".
                        p All business cases are stored in a repository, and comparisons can be made of the scores of multiple proposed business cases. 

                    details
                        summary Global "noticeboard" for seeking/offering engineering hours across offices (2020)
                        p This is a platform for two things: offering engineering personnel who aren't currently occupied not on project, and also for seeking engineering assistance when there is a shortfall. 
                        p For a global company with offices in multiple global regions, this platform helps in the situation where engineers have been freed up from projects but there is no work locally, and also the situation where a project's engineering effort requirements cannot be satisfied with the available resources within the local office. 
                        p Upon "posting" a seeking/offering notice on the platform for a particular skillset/department, a pre-formatted email is sent to selected representative of that skillset/department around the world. 
                        p Responses and follow ups are conducted outside of the platform via email. 

                    h5 2019
                    details
                        summary Site/office QHSE walkaround mobile app
                        p Mobile app designed for hand-held devices, for use during a leadership or management visit to an office or site, focussing on QHSE. This app replaces a paper checklist. 
                        p The questionnaire is filled out on the mobile device. Photos can be taken and appended to each question. At the end of the questionnaire, the results are pre-filled into PDF document which is sent to the QSHE administrator. 
                        p The PDF document is in the same layout as the paper checklist previously in use. 

                    details
                        summary Company bookmarks index
                        p An app to centrally house commonly used web links and software within the company. Other "official" methods were cumbersome and difficult to nevigate, and finding both engineering tools and corporate tools were not easy. 
                        p This app looks through a SharePoint list and uses a search box to quickly find the software of interest. The search box not only searches through the software title but also description body text also. 
                        p The source data in the SharePoint list is manually compiled. 
                        p There is facility in the app to allow users to submit their own pages. 

                    details
